---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Orange Chocolate Bakery, our story, values, and commitment to quality baked goods in Campbell, CA.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-chocolate to-cocoa text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-cream max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A passion for flavor, a commitment to quality
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-chocolate">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-chocolate/80 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Orange Chocolate Bakery was born from a simple belief: the best flavors come from unexpected combinations. The marriage of bright, citrusy orange with rich, comforting chocolate creates something truly magical.
            </p>
            <p>
              What started as a home kitchen experiment quickly became a passion project. After countless hours perfecting recipes and sharing treats with friends and family, Orange Chocolate Bakery officially opened as a California Cottage Food Operation in Campbell.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every loaf, cookie, and cake is handcrafted with premium ingredients and genuine care. We believe that baking is an art form that brings people together, and we're honored to be part of your special moments.
            </p>
            <p>
              From birthday celebrations to everyday indulgences, our mission is simple: create memorable experiences, one delicious bite at a time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-light to-orange-warm rounded-xl p-12 flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src={`${base}/images/ocb-logo.png`} alt="OCB Logo" class="w-full max-w-md drop-shadow-2xl" />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-center">
              <p class="text-chocolate font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">Freshly Baked Joy</p>
              <p class="text-chocolate/70">Campbell, California</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-chocolate">Our Values</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-warm/10 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-warm" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-chocolate">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-chocolate/70">
            We use only premium ingredients and never cut corners on quality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-warm/10 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-warm" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-chocolate">Made with Love</h3>
          <p class="text-chocolate/70">
            Every treat is handcrafted with passion and attention to detail.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-warm/10 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-warm" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-chocolate">Community Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-chocolate/70">
            Supporting local Campbell families and celebrating together.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-warm/10 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-warm" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-chocolate">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-chocolate/70">
            Exploring unique flavor combinations that surprise and delight.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Commitment Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cream to-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-chocolate">Our Commitment to You</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-warm/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">üåæ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-chocolate">Premium Ingredients</h4>
              <p class="text-chocolate/70">
                We source the finest chocolate, fresh oranges, and quality butter to ensure every bite is exceptional.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-warm/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">‚ú®</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-chocolate">Fresh Daily</h4>
              <p class="text-chocolate/70">
                All items are baked fresh to order. No preservatives, no shortcuts‚Äîjust pure, delicious goodness.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-warm/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">üè°</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-chocolate">Cottage Food Compliance</h4>
              <p class="text-chocolate/70">
                We operate under California's Cottage Food Law, ensuring safe food handling practices and proper labeling.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-warm/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">üíö</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-chocolate">Customer Satisfaction</h4>
              <p class="text-chocolate/70">
                Your happiness is our priority. We're not satisfied until you're delighted with every order.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Behind the Scenes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-chocolate">What Makes Us Different</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-chocolate/80">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-chocolate mb-4">The Perfect Balance</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            The combination of chocolate and orange isn't just thrown together‚Äîit's carefully balanced. We use fresh orange zest and juice to capture that bright citrus essence, paired with high-quality chocolate that brings depth and richness. The result is a harmonious blend that's become our signature.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-chocolate mb-4">Small Batch Excellence</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            As a cottage food operation, we're not a factory churning out thousands of units. Each order receives personal attention. This allows us to maintain exceptional quality control and customize orders to your preferences.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-chocolate mb-4">Supporting Local</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Based in Campbell, CA, we're proud to be part of this vibrant community. We source ingredients locally when possible and love being part of your celebrations, from birthdays to holidays to "just because" moments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-warm to-orange-light text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Experience OCB?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-10 text-white/90">
        Join the Orange Chocolate Bakery family and taste the difference that passion and quality make.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href={`${base}menu`} class="bg-white hover:bg-cream text-chocolate px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold transition shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          View Our Menu
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}order`} class="bg-chocolate hover:bg-cocoa text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold transition shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Place an Order
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
